main event: A UFO sighting occurred on 31 October 1966 in West Hyattsville, Maryland, where a witness described the object as being like a grayish donut.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 5-10 seconds,The observer reported seeing the object only on June 11, 1967, despite the event occurring in 1966,No physical evidence was found,The report concluded there was insufficient data for evaluation, and the photo associated with the case had insufficient clarity.
witness description: The witness was a male aged 19 who reported the sighting.
